</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_67" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_67_r1l11">Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_67_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Reẅſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l13">Plawen des <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu greẅcʒ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd wır eẅch in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l14"><expan>lecʒ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef ſchrıftlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l15">dınſtag nach ſand Merteins tag ſchıerıſt in eẅr ſtat gen Eger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l16">ſchıken <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von plawen <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> da ʒu hören vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l17"><expan>eincʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l18"><expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> Burkarten <expan>Reıkarcʒhof<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> weıſer dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> / Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l20">wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_67" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Rewsse<ex>n</ex></expan> von Plawen des
                            <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Grewcz, <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und wir ewch in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>lecz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief schriftlich
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan><app>
<note><q type="date"> auf den dinstag nach sand Merteins tag schierist</q>14.11.1419</note>
</app>in ewr stat gen Eger schiken <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Plawen <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> da
                        zu hören und <expan>einczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> Burkarten
                            <expan>Reikarczhof<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, weiser dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
